OL,3,C'Not equipped for this heat': Schools
OL,4,Cadapting as many close due to heatwave
OL,6,FA teacher in Sussex says his school is
OL,7,Fhaving to adapt as the heatwave
OL,8,Fcontinues to impact many across the
OL,9,FSouth East.
OL,11,FAl Jamieson, Assistant Head at St
OL,12,FAndrew's Primary School in Hove, says
OL,13,Fthey are thinking creatively to help
OL,14,Fsupport pupils.
OL,16,FThe school is open to children who are
OL,17,Fable to come in, but parents and
OL,18,Fcarers have been given the option to
OL,19,Fkeep them at home if they wish.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
