OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782461893
OL,3,C'Not equipped for this heat': Schools
OL,4,Cadapting as many close due to heatwave
OL,6,FIt comes as many schools across the
OL,7,Fregion are either shutting early or
OL,8,Fnot opening at all due to the extreme
OL,9,Fheat,
OL,11,FDiscussing how they will approach
OL,12,Ffuture warm weather, Mr Jamieson
OL,13,Fexplained: "I think it's something
OL,14,Fwe'll definitely have to think about
OL,15,Fmoving forwards.
OL,17,F"We're looking for advice from the
OL,18,Flocal authority about what steps we
OL,19,Fneed to take.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
