OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782461893
OL,3,C'Not equipped for this heat': Schools
OL,4,Cadapting as many close due to heatwave
OL,6,F"We're not really equipped in all
OL,7,Fhonesty for this heat, we don't have
OL,8,Fthe air conditioning, fans (are) only
OL,9,Ftouching the surface of what's needed.
OL,11,F"So yeah looking forward I think we're
OL,12,Fgoing to have some creative thinking,
OL,13,Fperhaps some more outside learning,
OL,14,Fsee if we can find shaded areas."
OL,16,FExplaining how the school's tackiling
OL,17,Fthe heat at the moment, Mr Jamieson
OL,18,Fadded: "It's a challenge, we're doing
OL,19,Flots of things we can to try and
OL,20,Fnegate the heat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782461893
OL,3,C'Not equipped for this heat': Schools
OL,4,Cadapting as many close due to heatwave
OL,6,F"Kids are obviously drinking lots of
OL,7,Fwater, there's less pressure on
OL,8,Flessons, we're taking it a.bit easier.
OL,10,FHe continued: "I don't think there's
OL,11,Fany magic solution, it is really hot.
OL,13,F"It's not something that's going to
OL,14,Flast hopefully past the weekend so I
OL,15,Fthink it's just being realistic with
OL,16,Four expectations of one another and
OL,17,Fjust getting through it really."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
